{
  "name": "Psychic Crush",
  "type": "spell",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>You overload the mind of one creature you can see within range, filling its psyche with discordant emotions. The target must make an Intelligence saving throw. On a failed save, the target takes [[/r 12d6]] psychic damage and is @condition[stunned] for 1 minute. On a successful save, the target takes half as much damage and isn't stunned.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>The stunned target can make an Intelligence saving throw at the end of each of its turns. On a successful save, the spell ends on the target.</p></div>",
